        "subject": "LU-3374 tests: Only import zpool if not present",
        "message": "LU-3374 tests: Only import zpool if not present\n\nOnly do zpool import if pool isn't already present, otherwise it will\nfail needlessly.  This fixes tests that do mount_facet and expect it\nto fail then run mount_facet again.\n\nOnly export pool if there are no datasets mounted from it.\n\nSigned-off-by: Nathaniel Clark <nathaniel.l.clark@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ia5eabc0bd78d628295c3cf85009315fdc9cce071\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
